Step 1: 1.	Log in to the lab server using the credential
Step2: Download Terraform Software 
https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/downloads
In this case I have used Amazon Linux 
``

Execute below command
sudo yum install -y yum-utils shadow-utils
sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/AmazonLinux/hashicorp.repo
sudo yum -y install terraform

Step3: validate software 
terraform --version

```
[ec2-user@ip-10-0-14-30 terraform]$ terraform --version
Terraform v1.4.6
on linux_amd64
+ provider registry.terraform.io/hashicorp/aws v4.66.0
```
